#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Badshah - Dear Aditya (Official Music Video) | Hiten
snippet.description:
A Letter To Myself

Audio Credits :
➟ Performed By Badshah
➟ Lyrics By Badshah
➟ Composed By  Badshah
➟ Music Produced By Hiten 
➟ Mixed & Mastered By Hiten
➟ Chorus Performed by Vaidik Dawale, Aanya Jain, Veda Mahajan & Advik Kasbe

Lyrics: 
Kaisa hai kya haal hai kya chal raha hai
Gaane vaane sun raha hai ya padh raha hai
Jitna marzi rishtedar tere peeche padein dekh
Dariyo na tu sapne dekh aur bade dekh
Ye jaankar tu aaj bada dang hoga
Ke pandran saal mein in sabka mooh band hoga
Jin teacheron ko tujhse zaraa bhi ummeed nai thi un saare teacheron ki naak mein dum

Papa ka thoda dhyaan rakh unka dil kamzor hai
Tere aas paas aadhe se zaada bande chor hain
Dost kam rakhiyo circle usse chota
Paisa boht aane wala hai wallet mota rakhiyo
Maa baap ke siva koi saga nai milega
Sukoon ghar ko chod kisi jagah nai milega
Jisko pyaar tu karega dil wo tera todegi
Kisi paise wale ke liye wo tujhe chodegi
Ek dedh hafta rona, man kare to chillana
Lekin fir chup chaap wapas music pe lag jaana
Uski yaad mein koi sad songs nahi banaiyo
Log waise hi boht rote hain tu party karaiyo

Koi dedh chaal chale to tu dhai samajhna
Par jo pakde tera hath use bhai samajhna
Par kain baar hath deke hathon ki lakeerein le jaate hain log tab hathon ki safai samajhna
Hateron ka dil dekh dehelte rahega
Shuru jaise marzi karaa ant keher se karega
2 kamron ke ghar mein tha janma tu tujhe pata nahi tu ek din kitne bade mahal mein rahega
Maa khush hogi lekin papa khush ni rahenge
Unka man hai tu IAS bane par push ni karenge
Log teri lagataar kaamyaabi dekh bore hoke hate karenge par mooh pe kuch ni kahenge

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Behkaave mein aake tu sidein switch nai karna
Fame ke chakkar mein kisiko diss nai karna
Khoob mehnat karna sirf wish nai karna
Aur jab saamne nishaana ho to miss nai karna
tujhe ladna hi hoga
Chahe kat jayen taangein aage badhna hi hog
Yaad rakh fame ek kiraaye ka makaan hai
Ek din tujhe ise khali karna hi hoga
jaam na sharaab lena, pyaar behisaab dena
Mooh kam kholiyo tu Kaam se jawaab dena
Banda tujhse kya chahe aankhon se bhaanp lena
Jo karega wo bharega khud ko na paap dena

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Joshi Kaka presents Sonu with potential matches, but she turns them all down. Meanwhile, Kanji Kaka does the same for Tapu. How will Tapu and Sonu handle this situation?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ⛏️ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie – only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.” The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: आज के बाद तुम हमारी रानी बनकर रहेगी | Yudh - Part 2 | Hema Malini, Danny Denzongpa
snippet.description:
युद्ध 1985 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की एक्शन थ्रिलर फिल्म है, जिसका निर्माण गुलशन राय ने किया है और यह उनके बेटे राजीव राय की निर्देशन की पहली फिल्म है। फिल्म में जैकी श्रॉफ, अनिल कपूर (दोहरी भूमिकाओं में), टीना मुनीम, प्राण, डैनी डेन्जोंगपा, नूतन, शत्रुघ्न सिन्हा और हेमा मालिनी सहित बड़ी स्टार कास्ट शामिल है।

Yudh  is a 1985 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film, produced by Gulshan Rai and marks the directorial debut of his son Rajiv Rai. The film features a large star cast including Jackie Shroff, Anil Kapoor (in dual roles), Tina Munim, Pran, Danny Denzongpa, Nutan, Shatrughan Sinha and Hema Malini.

Directed by : Rajiv Rai
Written by : K.A. Narayan, Rajiv Rai, Naeem Shah
Produced by : Gulshan Rai
Starring: Jackie Shroff, Anil Kapoor, Tina Munim, Pran, Danny Denzongpa, Nutan, Shatrughan Sinha, Hema Malini
Cinematography:  Romesh Bhalla
Edited by: Naresh Malhotra
Music by : Kalyanji Anandji
Distributed by: Trimurti Films
Release date : 3 May 1985

snippet.title: सुबह सुबह ऐसे दर्शन से आंखें तो धन्य हो गईं! 😜 Woh 7 Din - Anil Kapoor जबरदस्त Lotpot Comedy सीन
snippet.description:
वो सात दिन एक मजेदार फिल्म है जिसमें अनिल कपूर, पद्मिनी कोल्हापुरे और नसीरुद्दीन शाह की शानदार अदाकारी है। कहानी एक युवा लड़के की है जो अपने प्यार के लिए जीतोड़ मेहनत करता है। अनिल कपूर की मस्ती और पद्मिनी का दिलकश अंदाज इस फिल्म को और भी मजेदार बना देते हैं। नसीरुद्दीन शाह की हाजिरजवाबी के साथ, इस फिल्म के हास्य दृश्यों में आपको हंसी से लोटपोट कर देंगे। इसे देखना न भूलें!

Woh Saat Din is a hilarious film featuring the outstanding performances of Anil Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, and Naseeruddin Shah. The story revolves around a young man who goes to great lengths for his love. Anil Kapoor's antics and Padmini's charming presence add to the fun. With Naseeruddin Shah's wit, the comedy scenes will leave you in splits. Don't miss out on this entertaining ride!

Movie: Woh Saat Din (1983)
Cast: Anil Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, and Naseeruddin Shah
Director: Bapu
Music: Laxmikant–Pyarelal
Producer: Surinder Kapoor, Boney Kapoor

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

सचिन टिचकुले एक महत्वाकांक्षी ठेकेदार है जिसे घर और कार्यस्थल दोनों जगह हर किसी के विरोध का सामना करना पड़ता है। लेकिन वह संघर्ष करना जारी रखता है जबकि उसके परिवार के सदस्य गलत तरीके से कमाए गए पैसे को हड़पने में लगे रहते हैं।
मूवी - खट्टा मीठा (2010)
स्टार कास्ट: अक्षय कुमार, तृषा कृष्णन, जॉनी लीवर, राजपाल यादव, असरानी, ​​कुलभूषण खरबंदा, अरुणा ईरानी, ​​उर्वशी शर्मा, मिलिंद गुणाजी
निर्देशक - प्रियदर्शन

Dhamaal is about four friends afflicted by the get rich quick virus. Their fortunes take a turn after they accidentally bump into a victim who tells them about a hidden treasure who tells them about a hidden treasure in Goa including 10 crore rupees. The group race toward Goa in Contractors stolen car little knowing that their plans will soon be foiled albeit hilariously by Police Inspector Kabir Nayak - Sanjay Dutt.

Movie - Dhamaal
StarCast - Sanjay Dutt, Ritesh Deshmukh, Arshad Warsi, Jaaved Jaaferi, Asrani, Sanjay Mishra, Vijay Raaz, Tiku Talsania, Prem Chopra
Director - Indra Kumar

snippet.title: വെഞ്ഞാറമ്മൂട് കൂട്ടക്കൊല: ഷെമി ഭർത്താവ് അബ്ദുൾ റഹീമിനെ തിരിച്ചറിഞ്ഞതായി സുഹൃത്ത് അബുബക്കർ
snippet.description:
വെഞ്ഞാറമ്മൂട് കൂട്ടക്കൊലപാതക കേസിലെ പ്രതി അഫാന്‍റെ ആക്രമണത്തിൽ ഗുരുതര പരുക്കേറ്റ് ചികിത്സയിൽ കഴിയുന്ന ഷെമി ഭർത്താവ് അബ്ദുൾ റഹീമിനെ തിരിച്ചറിഞ്ഞതായി സുഹൃത്ത് അബുബക്കർ. മകന്‍ ബന്ധുവിന്‍റെ വീട്ടിലെന്നും കട്ടിലിൽ നിന്ന് വീണാണ് പരുക്കേറ്‍റതെന്നും ഷെമി പറഞ്ഞു. കൂടുതൽ ചോദിക്കുന്നത് ഇളയ മകനെക്കുറിച്ചെന്നും അബുബക്കർ മാധ്യമങ്ങളോട് പറഞ്ഞു.  നാട്ടിലെത്തിയ അബ്ദുപൾ റഹീം ഭാര്യയെ കണ്ടതിന് ശേഷം ബന്ധുക്കളുടെ ഖബറടക്കിയ പള്ളിയിലെത്തി .



വാർത്തകൾ തത്സമയം വിരൽത്തുമ്പിലെത്താൻ ഇന്നുതന്നെ ജനം ടിവി യുട്യൂബ് ചാനല്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യൂ.

snippet.description:
Get swept away by the riveting tale of "Ram Teri Ganga Maili" (1985). Director Raj Kapoor weaves a mesmerizing tapestry of forbidden love, betrayal and the relentless pursuit of hope against the backdrop of the tranquil Ganges. With spellbinding performances, soul-stirring melodies, and a narrative that tugs at your heartstrings. Brace yourself for an emotional rollercoaster that will leave you breathless.

Director: Raj Kapoor

Music : Ravindra Jain
Genre: Romance, Drama
Language: Hindi

snippet.title: Son of Sreenivasan Roast | Love Under Construction | Dhyan | Neeraj | Aju | Vishnu | Feb 28th
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves for the ultimate roast interview! Dhyan Sreenivasan takes the hot seat as the host of Son of Sreenivasan Roast, where he gets hilariously grilled alongside his guests—Neeraj Madhav, Aju Varghese, and Vishnu Raghav. Expect witty comebacks, savage burns, and non-stop laughter as they dish out jokes, share behind-the-scenes fun, and promote their upcoming web series Love Under Construction, streaming on JioHotstar from February 28.

Don't miss this riotous episode full of fun, banter, and unexpected twists!

Mehshar Episode 25 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nestle Bunyad - Imran Abbas - Neelam Muneer - 27th February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mehshar Digitally Presented by Nestle Bunyad

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated project, Mehshar, reunites the beloved on-screen duo of Imran Abbas and Neelam Muneer in a tale of love that promises to leave a mark on the viewers!

In Mehshar, love meets sacrifice as it follows the journey of a person who adores someone whose ambitions surpass all, leaving love behind. This is a story where love is selfless and giving is what matters most.

The story revolves around Abdur Rehman and Aima, cousins bound by a twist of fate. Their journey is not just about love, it’s about the emotions and sacrifices that truly make their bond special.

Is Abdur Rehman and Aima’s love destined to last forever, or will tragedy destroy it? Will their sacrifices and emotions elevate love to new heights? Will ambitions overpower love in this tale?

Is Abdur Rehman and Aima’s love destined to last forever, or will tragedy destroy it? Will their sacrifices and emotions elevate love to new heights? Will ambitions overpower love in this tale?

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4331 - Bhide ke Surprise se Ude Gada Family ke Hosh?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bhide Ka Surprise | Bhide dega Jhatka | Gokuldham Society

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.description:

Bajjo Episode 66 - [Eng Sub] - Javeria Saud - Arez Ahmed - Suqaynah Khan - 27th February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Bajjo is a heartfelt family drama that blends light-hearted moments with emotional turbulence. It portrays the struggles and conflicts of a middle-class household, where differences and arguments often take center stage.
Musarrat, fondly called Bajjo, is the eldest sibling, known for her sharp tongue and bitter demeanor. Her unmarried status fuels her frustration, leading to threats of drastic actions if anyone weds before her. This turmoil unsettles the entire family, but when a proposal finally comes her way, it brings its own set of challenges.
Will Bajjo ever find her match? Can her attitude change, or will it continue to cause problems for her family? Is her family’s patience running out, or will they stand by her despite her flaws? Can Bajjo overcome her struggles?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mazhar Moin
Writer: Javeria Saud
